Salam Tuan Karn!  - Memanggil!

00:20:35.600 --> 00:20:37.440
Salam Tuan Karn!  - Memanggil!

00:20:37.480 --> 00:20:39.520
Salam Tuan Karn!  - Memanggil!

00:20:39.560 --> 00:20:41.640
Salam Tuan Karn!  - Memanggil!

